VALUES
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01970', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '室內消防栓設備之屋頂水箱之水量，第一種消防栓有X立方公尺以上；第二種消防栓有Y立方公尺以上。 但與其他滅火設備並用時，水量應取其最大值，下列X，Y何者正確？', '["X=0.3，Y=0.5", "X=0.5，Y=0.3", "X=0.1，Y=0.3", "X=0.3，Y=0.1"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01971', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關開放式自動撒水設備之自動及手動啟動裝置，竣工時下列那一項規定錯誤？', '["自動啟動裝置，感知撒水頭或探測器動作後，能啟動一齊開放閥及加壓送水裝置", "自動啟動裝置，感知撒水頭使用標示溫度在79度以下者，且每20平方公尺設置1個；探測器使用定 溫式1種或2種，並依各類場所消防安全設備設置標準第120條規定設置，每一放水區域至少1個", "自動啟動裝置，感知撒水頭設在裝置面距樓地板面高度15公尺以下，且能有效探測火災處", "手動啟動裝置，手動啟動開關動作後，能啟動一齊開放閥及加壓送水裝置"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01972', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關泡沫滅火設備竣工時之流水檢知裝置，下列那一項規定錯誤？', '["各樓層之樓地板面積在3千平方公尺以下者，裝設1套，超過3千平方公尺者，裝設2套", "各樓層之樓地板面積在3千平方公尺以下者，裝設1套，超過3千平方公尺者，裝設2套；無隔間之 樓層內，前述3千平方公尺得增為6千平方公尺", "撒水頭或一齊開放閥開啟放水時，即發出警報", "附設制水閥，其高度距離樓地板面在1.5公尺以下0.8公尺以上，並於制水閥附近明顯易見處，設置標 明制水閥字樣之標識"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01973', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在測量室內消防栓設備之瞄子直線放水壓力時，應將含有皮托管及壓力計之壓力表進水口，放置於瞄子 前端瞄子口徑的多少距離處進行測量？', '["瞄子前端瞄子口徑的1倍處", "瞄子前端瞄子口徑的二分之一處", "瞄子前端瞄子口徑的三分之一處", "瞄子前端瞄子口徑的四分之一處"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01974', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在泡沫滅火設備進行性能檢查時，對於泡沫原液槽的檢查方法，下列那一項錯誤？', '["泡沫原液：打開原液槽之排液口制水閥，用燒杯或量筒採取泡沫原液（最好能由上、中、下3個位置 採液）", "泡沫原液：以目視確認所採取泡沫原液有無變質、污損", "壓力表：關掉表計之控制水閥將水排出，確認指針是否在1之位置；再打開表針控制水閥，操作啟動 裝置確認指針是否正常動作", "閥類：用手操作確認開、關動作是否容易進行"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01975', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '第三種乾粉滅火藥劑量，全區放射方式所需滅火藥劑量，每立方公尺防護區域所需滅火藥劑量(kg/m3)與 每平方公尺開口部所需追加滅火藥劑量(kg/m2)各為多少？', '["0.26、2.7", "0.36、2.7", "0.26、3.7", "0.36、3.7"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01976', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '乾粉滅火設備配管之設置規定，最低配管與最高配管間，落差在多少公尺以下？', '["35", "40", "50", "55"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-01977', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-103-a98764b7', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '加壓送水裝置之閥類應能承受幫浦最高揚水壓力多少倍以上壓力？且應具有耐熱及耐腐蝕性或具有同等 以上之性能者：', '["1.0", "1.5", "2.0", "2.5"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d33f08712e31", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5d173be7ea4b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103060", "c": "402", "s": "0710", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "水與化學系統消防安全設備概要", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年專門驗船師、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險員考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
